data.description: ****Back On the Market****This is a STUNNING  lovely Hesperia property that has super easy access to the I-15 Freeway and Hwy 395, making it commuter friendly! Large circular driveway, covered patio with double door entry into this spacious home. This MOVE-IN-READY! Good for the COMMUTER! Easy access to the freeway, close to restaurants and shops, great schools nearby, a lovely, peaceful neighborhood, and a sizable lot for storing all of your toys! The side gates are double-wide, allowing access for RV parking. The open floor plan has a cozy, welcoming interior that is drenched in natural light, a flowing living/dining area, and spacious entertainment areas. Stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a glass tile backsplash, modern cabinets, and recessed lighting are all features of this wonderfully outfitted kitchen, which has been tastefully remodel. Two spacious master bedrooms with modern bathrooms. With a spacious U-shaped driveway and a neatly maintained front yard, parking is no problem. Private entry through gates.Perfect for first time home buying opportunity don't miss out!
